      <title>星巴克提高美国门店薪酬后，咖啡行业用工正在重算：门店运营成本、效率与品牌竞争的新平衡</title>
      <link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-ti-gao-mei-guo-men-dian-xin-chou-hou-ka/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 05:45:38 +0800</pubDate>
